  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study is designed to evaluate the efficacy of a cigarette reduction intervention using a
      novel device called the Quitbit, a digital lighter paired with a smartphone mobile
      application, to enhance self-regulatory techniques for reducing cigarettes smoked per day
      toward cessation.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
